Ask HN: So I just had to transfer a chunk of change for kids college fund
text:
I am receiving a bunch of BS via email, text, calls, snail-mail...

HOW THE HECK IS THIS HAPPENING.

-

People talk about "controlling your online foot-print"

FUCK THAT.

How do I control Data Vampires?

--

Seriously - I moved money between three different accounts to get the money where it may serve my kid... BUT WHAT THE FUCK they were all SECURE banking transactions... How are all these creeps coming after me?

(yes I know that banks are selling my data, thats ___*NOT*___ what I am asking about:

I want a mechanism TO CONTROL my data seepage FROM BANKS. PLZ HALP.
